main event: An unidentified object was sighted over the vicinity between Davenport and Des Moines, Iowa on October 10, 1967.
interesting points: The object was reported to have appeared as a light that expanded to a solid form,The object changed in brightness and size during the sighting,No sound was reported,The sighting lasted for approximately 2 hours and 30 minutes,The object was described as white and brighter than the brightest stars.
sighted object: an unidentified light that became solid
witness description: The witness is a male aged 25.
